  Release flow (full doc in scripts/make-dmg.sh and README):
    1. Bump CFBundleShortVersionString + CFBundleVersion in the project.
    2. Run ./scripts/make-dmg.sh — prints sparkle:edSignature and length.
    3. Upload the DMG to a GitHub Release via gh release create.
    4. Add a new item block below (newest first) with those values + the
       GitHub release download URL, then commit + push this file.
  XML comments can not contain a double-hyphen sequence, so the literal
  shell flags are described in prose above.
-->
